## WebhostingApi

### Place Website Order
## Place Website Order
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/websites/order
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

