### Update Website IP DNS
## Update Website IP DNS
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/websites/{{id}}/buy_ip
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

{
 "ips": "<string>"
}


### Request Website Migration
## Request Website Migration
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/websites/{{id}}/migration
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

{
 "custPortal": "<string>",
 "regEmail": "<string>",
 "password": "<string>",
 "ctrlPanel": "<string>",
 "ftpUsername": "<string>",
 "ftpPassword": "<string>",
 "siteBusyMig": "<string>",
 "splReqMig": "<string>",
 "domainReg": "<string>",
 "dataMig": "<string>",
 "domainRegPortal": "<string>",
 "domainRegEmail": "<string>",
 "domainRegPassword": "<string>"
}


